name: THE DUKUH RETREAT - Pool Villa Guest House
address: Jalan Raya Pantai Pasut - Kerambitan Banjar Tibupoh, Belumbang, Kec. Kerambitan, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82161, Indonesia
review 1:
I stayed in the Dukuh Retreat for 7 days for yoga retreat and it was amazing! The room is spacious with two balconies, I loved eating at the back balcony facing the rice paddies. The service was great, it felt like I was on a vacation with family, Wayan and Komang looked after me so well. They took me to a mountain temple and to a traditional Balinese wedding giving me a taste of authentic local life.

I highly recommend The Dukuh Retreat for those looking for authentic, rural Bali experience with great accommodation and impeccable service.
review 2: What a brilliant place. What an interior, we took even pictures for our own house, what a kitchen, even more tasteful, so delicious. So much space for us as a Dutch family. Nice pool, beautiful view. Nice people. We slept very well.
review 3: Beautiful and pleasant place. Good family business. Good massage)Good breakfast, good service)
review 4: We had a wonderful stay at the Dukuh retreat. Rooms are very nice, clean and the beds were excellent. The atmosphere is very relaxing with a beautiful garden and a pool with a view. Most importantly all staff was very friendly and made us feel sad to leave. Whether it is breakfast, lunch or dinner: very delicious. Enak! Highly recommended!
review 5: Wow, I enjoyed this Place so much. The Family gives a warm welcoming feeling. The Food is super. I took a package with Yoga everyday. Tedy the Instractor is awesome, I had everyday a Massage and a Program to join, like Visiting The Shaman or Cycling to the Beach and Cooking Class. Everything was great. The loving owners would to anything to make you happy and relaxed. Please visit this Retreat and you will be feeling great.
